      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>春节大促活动页</title>\n<style>\n    :root {\n        --red: #D0021B;\n        --gold: #FFD700;\n        --light-gray: #F4F4F5;\n        --white: #FFFFFF;\n        --dark: #333333;\n    }\n    * {\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\n    }\n    body {\n        font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n        background-color: var(--light-gray);\n        color: var(--dark);\n        line-height: 1.6;\n    }\n    header, section, nav, aside, footer {\n        padding: 20px;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n        background-color: var(--white);\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n    }\n    .hero-section {\n        background-color: var(--red);\n        color: var(--white);\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 40px 20px;\n    }\n    .hero-section h1 {\n        font-size: 2rem;\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    .hero-section p {\n        font-size: 1.1rem;\n    }\n    h2, h3, h4 {\n        color: var(--red);\n        margin-bottom: 10px;\n    }\n    p {\n        font-size: 1rem;\n    }\n    .price-box {\n        background-color: var(--gold);\n        color: var(--dark);\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .promo-banner {\n        background-color: var(--red);\n        color: var(--white);\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    nav.category-list {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-direction: column;\n        align-items: flex-start;\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: var(--dark);\n        color: var(--white);\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    @media (min-width: 768px) {\n        body {\n            padding: 20px;\n        }\n        .layout-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        nav.category-list {\n            flex-direction: row;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n        }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n<section class=\"hero-section\" id=\"hero-section\">\n    <h1>春节年货大促销 - 喜迎新春</h1>\n    <p>浓浓的节日氛围，限时优惠，囤好年货迎新年！</p>\n</section>\n\n<div class=\"layout-grid\">\n    <div>\n        <section class=\"product-specs\" id=\"product-specs\">\n            <h2>组合装规格 - 多口味精选</h2>\n            <p>丰富搭配，满足全家人的味蕾，份量足，性价比高。</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"price-box\" id=\"price-box\">\n            <h3>现价 ¥199<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through; margin-left:10px;\">¥299</span></h3>\n            <p>立省33%，立即下单享受优惠！</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"promo-banner\" id=\"promo-banner\">\n            <h4>限时抢购 - 剩余2天</h4>\n            <p>年货必备 · 热销推荐</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"channel-flow\" id=\"channel-flow\">\n            <h4>选择购买数量</h4>\n            <p>挑选数量后加入购物车，轻松结算。</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"coupon-zone\" id=\"coupon-zone\">\n            <h4>领取优惠券</h4>\n            <p>满100减20，领取后结算自动抵扣。</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"trust-badges\" id=\"trust-badges\">\n            <h4>品牌保障</h4>\n            <p>正品保证，快速发货，放心购买。</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <aside class=\"cart-panel\" id=\"cart-panel\">\n        <h4>购物车管理</h4>\n        <p>查看已选商品，可修改数量或删除。</p>\n    </aside>\n</div>\n\n<nav class=\"category-list\" id=\"category-list\">\n    <h4>商品分类</h4>\n    <p>浏览更多年货零食、美味特产。</p>\n</nav>\n\n<footer id=\"footer\">\n    <h4>联系客服与售后政策</h4>\n    <p>支持多种支付方式，保障您的购物体验。</p>\n</footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"
